<div dir="ltr"><div>HI Folks, Team Ninja have been testing and fixing. First off, thanks to all the people who posted issues or patches to either github or the forums. <br><br></div><div>There are 32 categories of bug fixes which include more Github issues in each of the buckets. Some of the big items include Twitter and media fixes, CSV Uploads, login issues and more.<br>

<br></div><div>There are two types of help needed:<br></div><div>1. Download the latest from Github<br></div><div> 2. Use our <a href="http://testing.ushahidi.com">testing.ushahidi.com</a> instance (This uses the same code that will end up on Crowdmap Classic and Ushahidi platform)<br>

<br></div><div>Some ways to help:<br><br></div><div>We are hosting a Community Test day on August 27, 2013. Join us online -Skype or IRC to co-test. Bug fixers are very welcome too!  <br></div><div><br></div><div>1. Test Basic Functionality <br>

